    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎走进属于你的电竞俱乐部！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你需要组建并经营一支属于你的职业电竞战队，在海量的选手中挑选最符合你要求的人选，为他们安排日程，提升实力。在策略和经营中，体验一支电竞战队从零开始走上世界赛巅峰的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/1d394280eee4d3cea8c13fc4112f8d1e.poster.avif?t=1771902478\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/1d394280eee4d3cea8c13fc4112f8d1e.webm?t=1771902478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/1d394280eee4d3cea8c13fc4112f8d1e.mp4?t=1771902478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >策略与经营的双重挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经营战队并非易事，你会不断面临金钱匮乏、投资失败、教练出走、选手离开……你将如何走过这条满是荆棘的道路？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/aa6b291e8dbaf0f1c1ee6a4b357b3c22.poster.avif?t=1771902478\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/aa6b291e8dbaf0f1c1ee6a4b357b3c22.webm?t=1771902478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/aa6b291e8dbaf0f1c1ee6a4b357b3c22.mp4?t=1771902478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >命运的馈赠与考验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，幸运的你也会偶遇天降横财、友人协助、追求者示爱、投资人青睐……你要如何守住最初那份对电竞的热情？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/336038e257b5486c9e1adb688049a809.poster.avif?t=1771902478\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/336038e257b5486c9e1adb688049a809.webm?t=1771902478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/336038e257b5486c9e1adb688049a809.mp4?t=1771902478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/cdff30bac3f8756c00c47ae1826c6164.poster.avif?t=1771902478\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/cdff30bac3f8756c00c47ae1826c6164.webm?t=1771902478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/cdff30bac3f8756c00c47ae1826c6164.mp4?t=1771902478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌控战队与人生的结局</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最终，你的战队将问鼎世界赛冠军，还是黯然神伤退却赛场；你的生活是锦衣玉食腰缠万贯，还是负债累累最终破产；你的感情是与相爱之人相濡以沫，还是纸醉金迷风花雪月……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/9e5dab76c43ef9a373a2275e7e7820c8.poster.avif?t=1771902478\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/9e5dab76c43ef9a373a2275e7e7820c8.webm?t=1771902478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013150/extras/9e5dab76c43ef9a373a2275e7e7820c8.mp4?t=1771902478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >命运之轮停驻的地方，取决于你的每一次的抉择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方粉丝Q群①群：1017990505</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方客服QQ：3516398578</p>",
